<div>T&#7915; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7871;n nay, tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H Th&#259;ng Long v&#7851;n lu&#244;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&#224; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng ng&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam. V&#7899;i trang thi&#7871;t b&#7883; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, c&#249;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; tr&#7867; trung, h&#432;&#7899;ng t&#7899;i s&#7921; ti&#7879;n nghi v&#224; tho&#7843;i m&#225;i c&#7911;a sinh vi&#234;n, h&#236;nh &#7843;nh c&#7911;a tr&#432;&#7901;ng Th&#259;ng Long lu&#244;n khi&#7871;n c&#225;c b&#7841;n tr&#7867; ph&#7843;i xu&#253;t xoa v&#224; ghen t&#7883; v&#7899;i sinh vi&#234;n ng&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#224;y. Th&#7901;i gian v&#7915;a qua, tr&#432;&#7901;ng Th&#259;ng Long l&#7841;i c&#224;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n qua cu&#7897;c thi Gi&#7885;ng h&#225;t Vi&#7879;t 2015, v&#7899;i s&#7921; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n c&#7911;a gi&#225;m kh&#7843;o, ca s&#297; Tu&#7845;n H&#432;ng- m&#7897;t c&#7921;u sinh vi&#234;n c&#7911;a tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#224; b&#7841;n Anh Duy, sinh vi&#234;n c&#7911;a tr&#432;&#7901;ng, top 4 team Thu Ph&#432;&#417;ng.</div><div><br></div>T&#7885;a l&#7841;c tr&#234;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Nghi&#234;m Xu&#226;n Y&#234;m, H&#224; N&#7897;i, tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H Th&#259;ng Long tuy kh&#244;ng c&#243; di&#7879;n t&#237;ch qu&#225; r&#7897;ng, nh&#432;ng l&#7841;i c&#243; khu&#244;n vi&#234;n c&#361;ng nh&#432; ki&#7871;n tr&#250;c thu&#7897;c h&#224;ng top trong s&#7889; c&#225;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H t&#7841;i H&#224; N&#7897;i. B&#7841;n s&#7869; ng&#7841;c nhi&#234;n khi bi&#7871;t r&#7857;ng, &#273;&#7875; theo h&#7885;c t&#7841;i &#273;&#226;y, b&#7841;n kh&#244;ng nh&#7845;t thi&#7871;t ph&#7843;i c&#243; m&#7897;t &quot;h&#7847;u bao kh&#7911;ng khi&#7871;p&quot;. V&#7899;i 3 k&#7923; h&#7885;c/n&#259;m v&#224; ti&#7873;n h&#7885;c m&#7895;i k&#7923; trung b&#236;nh l&#224; t&#7915; 6-10 tri&#7879;u. Tu&#7923; theo s&#7889; m&#244;n v&#224; t&#237;n ch&#7881; c&#7911;a t&#7915;ng sinh vi&#234;n m&#224; m&#7897;t n&#259;m h&#7885;c, m&#7913;c h&#7885;c ph&#237; s&#7869; dao &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; 20-15 tri&#7879;u. &#273;&#226;y l&#224; m&#7897;t m&#7913;c ti&#7873;n h&#7885;c kh&#244;ng qu&#225; &#273;&#7855;t &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7885;c trong m&#7897;t m&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng ho&#224;n h&#7843;o, &#273;&#7865;p ng&#7845;t ng&#226;y nh&#432; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H Th&#259;ng Long.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div>&#272;&#432;&#7907;c sinh vi&#234;n quen g&#7885;i v&#7899;i c&#225;i t&#234;n th&#226;n m&#7853;t TLU, b&#432;&#7899;c ch&#226;n v&#224;o khu&#244;n vi&#234;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H Th&#259;ng Long, nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i r&#7845;t d&#7877; l&#7847;m t&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;ang b&#432;&#7899;c v&#224;o m&#7897;t tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H &#7903; n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i v&#7899;i c&#7843;nh quan th&#417; m&#7897;ng, y&#234;n &#7843;. Tr&#234;n s&#226;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng, h&#236;nh &#7843;nh v&#224;i ch&#250; b&#7891; c&#226;u &#273;ang r&#7881;a c&#225;nh, g&#249; g&#249; g&#7885;i nhau g&#7907;i c&#7843;m gi&#225;c th&#7853;t y&#234;n b&#236;nh. M&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng &#432;u ti&#234;n h&#224;ng &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a nh&#224; tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&#224; kh&#244;ng nh&#7919;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o c&#7843;nh quan &#273;&#7865;p, m&#224; c&#242;n ph&#7843;i th&#226;n thi&#7879;n v&#7899;i thi&#234;n nhi&#234;n. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#243; m&#7897;t khu v&#432;&#7901;n ri&#234;ng cho sinh vi&#234;n &#244;n b&#224;i, t&#225;n g&#7851;u, ho&#7863;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c c&#225;c ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng ngo&#7841;i kh&#243;a. Ngo&#224;i ra, &#272;H Th&#259;ng Long c&#242;n n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng l&#224; m&#7897;t ng&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng nhi&#7873;u hoa. L&#250;c n&#224;o c&#361;ng d&#7877; d&#224;ng b&#7855;t g&#7863;p c&#225;c kh&#243;m hoa &#273;a s&#7855;c, vui m&#7855;t, t&#259;ng th&#234;m v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p cho ng&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0606-771c6.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0606-771c6"></div><div style="text-align:center"><i>M&#7897;t g&#243;c khu&#244;n vi&#234;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H Th&#259;ng Long.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><div><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0628-35246.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0628-35246"></div><div><br></div><div><div><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0630-8c7c0.jpg" w="1500" h="2250" alt="DSC_0630-8c7c0"></div><div><br></div><div><div><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0633-98d13.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0633-98d13"></div><div><br></div><div><div><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0649-4ef4c.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0649-4ef4c"></div><i>V&#432;&#7901;n sinh vi&#234;n, &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7871;n &#432;a th&#237;ch &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c s&#225;ch, t&#225;n g&#7851;u, ch&#417;i &#273;&#224;n...</i><br><br></div><div><div><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0648-cca91.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0648-cca91"></div><i>C&#7893;ng hoa, &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m pose h&#236;nh n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng c&#7911;a d&#226;n TLU.</i></div></div></div><div><i><br></i></div></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div>&#272;i&#7875;m c&#7897;ng n&#7919;a c&#7911;a ng&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#224;y l&#224; c&#417; s&#7903; v&#7853;t ch&#7845;t v&#244; c&#249;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i. B&#234;n c&#7841;nh ph&#242;ng h&#7885;c, c&#225;c ph&#242;ng ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng... sinh vi&#234;n TLU c&#242;n t&#7921; h&#224;o v&#7899;i m&#7897;t h&#7897;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7899;n hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i v&#7899;i m&#224;n h&#236;nh 4k led tr&#7883; gi&#225; h&#224;ng t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng, hay ph&#242;ng t&#7853;p gym d&#224;nh ri&#234;ng cho sinh vi&#234;n v&#224; c&#225;n b&#7897;, gi&#225;o vi&#234;n trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng. Ch&#432;a k&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng khu th&#7875; ch&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i v&#224; c&#7921;c k&#7923; r&#7897;ng r&#227;i, hay s&#226;n b&#243;ng r&#7893; &#273;&#7865;p long lanh m&#224; b&#7841;n th&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7845;y trong nh&#7919;ng b&#7897; phim H&#224;n Qu&#7889;c.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0612-6ce61.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0612-6ce61"></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i>Khu th&#7875; ch&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u m&#244;n h&#7885;c cho sinh vi&#234;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0613-978d1.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0613-978d1"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0617-258c3.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0617-258c3"></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i>S&#226;n b&#243;ng r&#7893;, ni&#7873;m t&#7921; h&#224;o c&#7911;a d&#226;n TLU, n&#417;i t&#7915;ng di&#7877;n ra nhi&#7873;u gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7845;u cho sinh vi&#234;n.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0654-fe17b.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0654-fe17b"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0660-861e5.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0660-861e5"></div><span style="font-style: italic;">Canteen c&#7911;a tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#361;ng s&#7841;ch v&#224; &#273;&#7865;p lung linh.</span></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align: left;">Sinh vi&#234;n c&#225;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&#432;&#7901;i nh&#7845;t kho&#7843;n m&#242; ra ngo&#224;i c&#7893;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#236;m h&#224;ng v&#259;n ph&#242;ng ph&#7849;m hay ti&#7879;m photocopy. &#7902; tr&#432;&#7901;ng Th&#259;ng Long, b&#7841;n &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n l&#224; ch&#7881; c&#7847;n &#273;i xu&#7889;ng s&#226;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng. C&#243; h&#7859;n m&#7897;t &quot;khu ph&#7889;&quot; nho nh&#7887; v&#7899;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; nh&#7919;ng h&#224;ng photo, in &#7845;n, hi&#7879;u b&#225;n s&#225;ch v&#7903;,... trang b&#7883; t&#7853;n r&#259;ng cho nh&#7919;ng nhu c&#7847;u d&#249; l&#224; nh&#7887; nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a &#273;&#225;m sinh vi&#234;n.&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0669-bd932.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0669-bd932"></div><br><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0672-c9979.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0672-c9979"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0678-f5c2f.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0678-f5c2f"></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i>Khu&#244;n vi&#234;n mang d&#225;ng c&#7845;p c&#225;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0680-8e496.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0680-8e496"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0682-447f2.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0682-447f2"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0684-bf89b.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0684-bf89b"></div><div style="text-align:center"><i>Khu h&#7897;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng-gi&#7843;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t trong h&#7897;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#243; m&#224;n h&#236;nh 4k led hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i tr&#7883; gi&#225; h&#224;ng t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0687-f5575.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0687-f5575"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0692-9430c.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0692-9430c"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0695-58e53.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0695-58e53"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0699-a1d65.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0699-a1d65"></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i>Khu t&#7893; h&#7907;p th&#432; vi&#7879;n- ph&#242;ng m&#225;y- ph&#242;ng &#273;&#7885;c- ph&#242;ng t&#7921; h&#7885;c.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0705-5d36f.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0705-5d36f"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0710-1f6bf.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0710-1f6bf"></div><div style="text-align:center"><i>Khu&#244;n vi&#234;n &#273;&#7847;y hoa c&#7911;a nh&#224; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0712-d6abd.jpg" w="1500" h="2250" alt="DSC_0712-d6abd"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0716-1f48c.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0716-1f48c"></div><div style="text-align:center"><i>Gi&#7919; im l&#7863;ng- Th&#244;ng &#273;i&#7879;p th&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7845;y tr&#234;n c&#225;c h&#224;nh lang l&#7899;p h&#7885;c.</i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><br></i></div><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0717-51977.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0717-51977"></div><div style="text-align:center"><br></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i><div style="text-align:center"><img src="https://kenh14cdn.com/thumb_w/600/3f38be05d0/2015/09/05/DSC_0719-024ce.jpg" w="1500" h="1000" alt="DSC_0719-024ce"></div></i><div style="text-align:center"><i>Ph&#242;ng h&#7885;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i v&#7899;i s&#7913;c ch&#7913;a 40-80 sinh vi&#234;n.</i></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>


